Povedz mi všetko, 
 čo ti leží na srdci.

128
00:14:37,060 --> 00:14:38,740
<i>Mama.</i>

129
00:14:39,510 --> 00:14:41,010
<i>Mama.</i>

130
00:14:52,010 --> 00:14:53,590
